title: Ep. 386 - The Misogynistic Left
description:
A man sues immigrant women to force her to wax his genitals, and Miss World USA dethrones Miss Michigan for refusing to wear a hijab. We examine how the Left came to embrace misogyny. Then, AOC endorses open borders, and President Trump unveils the greatest new merch of the 2020 campaign. Date: 07-23-2019
